{"tid":740753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【九巴刺針】刺針狂徒又出沒 男乘客被拮臀部受傷","createTime":"2018-07-13T06:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T08:01:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9a6f9f1fa6a3dccf9bd2f25ae1331a89c27f9db8","tid":740753,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:31:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180713/large/1531462968_bc3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180713%2Flarge%2F1531462968_bc3f.jpg&h=c9108298&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴藏針案，警方雖然拘捕一名30歲無業男，惟仍未有杜絕兇徒「落針」，中午1時許，904號路線九巴，行至旺角彌敦道749號對開，一名男乘客報稱座位藏針，他被刺傷臀部，他通知車長，車長報警求助。警員到場調查，事主送院敷治。<br />\n<br />\n九巴刺針案有新進展，沙田重案組經深入調查後，探員本月4日於青衣長發邨亮發樓拘捕一名30歲無業男子，涉嫌與其中3案有關(相關連結︰ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2tBZSfB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2tBZSfB&d=9LqqMbCbXTfEuUTDu09WMSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0329106e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2tBZSfB</a> )。警方表示，疑犯不滿九巴飛站而犯案，在其家中搜出7支縫紉針，與九巴座位上撿獲的一致。警方正調查其餘6宗案件，不排除再有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180713/58437368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180713%2F58437368&d=9LqqMbCbXTfEuUTDu09WMSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=df3eb078\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180713%2F58437368&h=8c06e97a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180713/58437368</a>"},{"pid":"902796e3967da08c55e40734bb975f01031620b8","tid":740753,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"又是旦拉件人交數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7aa4273755f9faf2bad95e809c99da9081bd38d","tid":740753,"uid":77196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"902796e3967da08c55e40734bb975f01031620b8","tid":740753,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"又是旦拉件人交數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:37:19.000Z","msg":"警犬不嬲都係，諗住捉到一件之後有威嚇作用冇人敢再出黎玩野，舊果堆可以入哂條友數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f487479a4900b2bdb91b6341453cbd929ec18806","tid":740753,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:58:12.000Z","msg":"而家香港咁多警犬<br />\n<br />\n但又捉唔到人, 以後一車一警犬駐守<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff30f49fd7c3c59947a8ff8fcc98e6637eb5699c","tid":740753,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:11:30.000Z","msg":"大把痴線佬日日得閒無事同你拮針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72847cda352e5c8b9c235e199608cc595bfef453","tid":740753,"uid":65847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff30f49fd7c3c59947a8ff8fcc98e6637eb5699c","tid":740753,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:11:30.000Z","msg":"大把痴線佬日日得閒無事同你拮針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:25:19.000Z","msg":"捉到一個仲有千千萬萬個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ca214e162ff202e5f2d160ee6df244999136ad","tid":740753,"uid":75845,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:28:59.000Z","msg":"大肆報導完其實個個都可以